    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/6df5db1fbdff549fb3a40a86d143bbd6.avif?t=1745628078\" width=800 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up to 8 players spawn in an enclosed arena where they must battle it out.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Taking damage results in increased knockback. Don't get hit out of the arena!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Obtaining rifts will grant players new weapons, spawn events, or give deadly curses.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For each round you survive,  you get money to help secure your victory!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/44dfa51d124224b80982ba06ae3170ad.poster.avif?t=1745628078\" width=288 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/44dfa51d124224b80982ba06ae3170ad.webm?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/44dfa51d124224b80982ba06ae3170ad.mp4?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/4510f7f146b6df2f4f51ece9b808a4e9.poster.avif?t=1745628078\" width=288 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093880/extras/4510f7f146b6df2f4f51ece9b808a4e9.webm?t=1745628078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st